gujarati.context:
Dharma's destruction has occurred, that's the reason;
I will make it bright again, that's the reason.

Alone, the true path is; I will establish it with my love.

Here is the translation:

That person's path is the one that he will make go, as it goes; 
He came from hardship and that will bloom; 

Body though not be affected by pain, at the end it will get happiness.

Here is the translation:

We are in foreign land, our situation is very poor; 
The oppressed ones have become apocalyptic and vast, our fortune has arrived with Sri Viraj Mocha.

This is what that says:

"This man gave Sri Krishna's respect, then we took this life; 
You people met with the great king there, he pleased us today."
